<h3>WebSockets</h3>

<button {{action 'buttonClicked'}} class="btn btn-primary">Send</button>

<h3>Public Channels</h3>

<button {{action 'subscribeButton'}} class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe</button>
<button {{action 'unsubscribeButton'}} class="btn btn-primary">Unsubscribe</button>

<p>Click the "Subscribe" button to connect to a WebSocket channel named "public_test" provided by the Rails server. In another browser tab,  go to <a href="//localhost:3000/public_channel">localhost:3000/public_channel</a>. For every GET request at this URL, an alert will be fired on this page until the "Unsubscribe" button is clicked.</p>

<h3>Private Channels</h3>

<button {{action 'privateSubscribeButton'}} class="btn btn-primary">Private Subscribe</button>
<button {{action 'privateUnsubscribeButton'}} class="btn btn-primary">Private Unsubscribe</button>

<p>Click the "Private Subscribe" button to connect to a WebSocket channel named "private_test" provided by the Rails server. In another browser tab,  go to <a href="//localhost:3000/private_channel">localhost:3000/private_channel</a>. For every GET request at this URL, an alert will be fired on this page until the "Private Unsubscribe" button is clicked.</p>
